 that is stimulated.

180
00:07:58,710 --> 00:08:01,279
 It's like causing
 temporary brain damage.

181
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,147
 But as soon as
 the pulse is over,

182
00:08:03,148 --> 00:08:05,716
